* Language Features

* Language Features

- Cross platform, natively compiled
- Produces a single executable
- Statically typed
- Garbage collected

* Language Features

- Concurrency
- Composable types
- Interfaces satisfied implicitly
- Capital letter = exported
- Return multiple values

* Language Omissions

- Generics
- Overloads
- Implicit type conversions

