* $GOPATH

- **Go*source*lives*best*under*$GOPATH*
- Example: **~/go/src/github.com/name/repo*

  export GOPATH=$HOME/go

Include bin directories in `PATH`:

  export PATH=$PATH:$GOROOT/bin:$GOPATH/bin

